{
  "video_id": "r_qYQXRVP0k",
  "title": "Amanda Bennett: We need a heroic narrative for death",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12498.0,
      "end_time": 15157.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like you to come back with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15157.0,
      "end_time": 17580.0,
      "text": "just for a few minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17580.0,
      "end_time": 19927.0,
      "text": "to a dark night in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19927.0,
      "end_time": 22648.0,
      "text": "the night I met my husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22648.0,
      "end_time": 26910.0,
      "text": "It was a city so long ago that it was still called"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26910.0,
      "end_time": 28204.0,
      "text": "Peking."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28204.0,
      "end_time": 30825.0,
      "text": "So I went to a party."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30825.0,
      "end_time": 34208.0,
      "text": "I sat down next to a stout, middle-aged man"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34208.0,
      "end_time": 37722.0,
      "text": "with owl glasses and a bow tie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37722.0,
      "end_time": 40615.0,
      "text": "and he turned out to be a Fulbright scholar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40615.0,
      "end_time": 44179.0,
      "text": "there in China specifically to study"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44179.0,
      "end_time": 46270.0,
      "text": "Sino-Soviet relations."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46270.0,
      "end_time": 48670.0,
      "text": "What a gift it was to the eager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48670.0,
      "end_time": 51428.0,
      "text": "young foreign correspondent that I was then."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51428.0,
      "end_time": 53436.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d pump him for information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53436.0,
      "end_time": 55930.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m mentally scribbling notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55930.0,
      "end_time": 57402.0,
      "text": "for the stories I plan to write."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57402.0,
      "end_time": 59887.0,
      "text": "I talk to him for hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59887.0,
      "end_time": 63398.0,
      "text": "Only months later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63398.0,
      "end_time": 65772.0,
      "text": "I discover who he really was."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65772.0,
      "end_time": 68545.0,
      "text": "He was the China representative"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68545.0,
      "end_time": 72774.0,
      "text": "for the American Soybean Association."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72774.0,
      "end_time": 76440.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t understand. Soybeans?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76440.0,
      "end_time": 78798.0,
      "text": "You told me you were a Fulbright scholar.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78799.0,
      "end_time": 80687.0,
      "text": "\"Well, how long would you have talked to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80687.0,
      "end_time": 82729.0,
      "text": "if I told you we&#39;re in soybeans?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82729.0,
      "end_time": 85210.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85210.0,
      "end_time": 88502.0,
      "text": "I said, \"You jerk.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88502.0,
      "end_time": 92255.0,
      "text": "Only jerk wasn&#39;t the word I used."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92255.0,
      "end_time": 96402.0,
      "text": "I said, \"You could&#39;ve gotten me fired.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96402.0,
      "end_time": 99939.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Let&#39;s get married.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99939.0,
      "end_time": 101226.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101226.0,
      "end_time": 104122.0,
      "text": "\"Travel the world and have lots of kids.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104122.0,
      "end_time": 106220.0,
      "text": "So we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106220.0,
      "end_time": 108265.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108265.0,
      "end_time": 113507.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113507.0,
      "end_time": 117247.0,
      "text": "And what an alive man Terence Bryan Foley"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117247.0,
      "end_time": 118694.0,
      "text": "turned out to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118694.0,
      "end_time": 120337.0,
      "text": "He was a Chinese scholar"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120337.0,
      "end_time": 122203.0,
      "text": "who later, in his 60s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122203.0,
      "end_time": 124755.0,
      "text": "got a Ph.D. in Chinese history."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124755.0,
      "end_time": 127243.0,
      "text": "He spoke six languages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127243.0,
      "end_time": 129731.0,
      "text": "he played 15 musical instruments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129731.0,
      "end_time": 131507.0,
      "text": "he was a licensed pilot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131507.0,
      "end_time": 134678.0,
      "text": "he had once been a San Francisco cable car operator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134678.0,
      "end_time": 137512.0,
      "text": "he was an expert in swine nutrition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137512.0,
      "end_time": 141293.0,
      "text": "dairy cattle, Dixieland jazz, film noir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 141293.0,
      "end_time": 145477.0,
      "text": "and we did travel the country, and the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145477.0,
      "end_time": 147706.0,
      "text": "and we did have a lot of kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147706.0,
      "end_time": 149447.0,
      "text": "We followed my job, and it seemed like"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149448.0,
      "end_time": 153150.0,
      "text": "there was nothing that we couldn&#39;t do."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153150.0,
      "end_time": 156797.0,
      "text": "So when we found the cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156797.0,
      "end_time": 159362.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t seem strange to us at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 159362.0,
      "end_time": 161995.0,
      "text": "that without saying a word to each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161995.0,
      "end_time": 164421.0,
      "text": "we believed that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164421.0,
      "end_time": 166679.0,
      "text": "if we were smart enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166680.0,
      "end_time": 171110.0,
      "text": "and strong enough and brave enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171110.0,
      "end_time": 173484.0,
      "text": "and we worked hard enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173484.0,
      "end_time": 178762.0,
      "text": "we could keep him from dying ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178762.0,
      "end_time": 182261.0,
      "text": "And for years, it seemed like we were succeeding."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182261.0,
      "end_time": 185140.0,
      "text": "The surgeon emerged from the surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185140.0,
      "end_time": 187416.0,
      "text": "What&#39;d he say? He said what surgeons always say:"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 187417.0,
      "end_time": 189419.0,
      "text": "\"We got it all.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189419.0,
      "end_time": 192462.0,
      "text": "Then there was a setback when the pathologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 192462.0,
      "end_time": 194834.0,
      "text": "looked at the kidney cancer closely."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194835.0,
      "end_time": 196464.0,
      "text": "It turned out to be a rare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196464.0,
      "end_time": 198273.0,
      "text": "exceedingly aggressive type,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198273.0,
      "end_time": 201355.0,
      "text": "with a diagnosis that was almost universally fatal"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 201355.0,
      "end_time": 203745.0,
      "text": "in several weeks at most."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 203746.0,
      "end_time": 207456.0,
      "text": "And yet, he did not die."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 207456.0,
      "end_time": 210965.0,
      "text": "Mysteriously, he lived on."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 210966.0,
      "end_time": 213500.0,
      "text": "He coached Little League for our son."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213500.0,
      "end_time": 215602.0,
      "text": "He built a playhouse for our daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 215602.0,
      "end_time": 218676.0,
      "text": "And meanwhile, I&#39;m burying myself in the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218676.0,
      "end_time": 220350.0,
      "text": "looking for specialists."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 220350.0,
      "end_time": 222911.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m looking for a cure."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222911.0,
      "end_time": 224988.0,
      "text": "So a year goes by"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 224988.0,
      "end_time": 228194.0,
      "text": "before the cancer, as cancers do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228194.0,
      "end_time": 230194.0,
      "text": "reappears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 230194.0,
      "end_time": 232269.0,
      "text": "and with it comes another death sentence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 232270.0,
      "end_time": 234463.0,
      "text": "this time nine months."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 234463.0,
      "end_time": 238477.0,
      "text": "So we try another treatment, aggressive, nasty."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 238477.0,
      "end_time": 240297.0,
      "text": "It makes him so sick, he has to quit it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 240297.0,
      "end_time": 243314.0,
      "text": "yet still he lives on."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 243314.0,
      "end_time": 245209.0,
      "text": "Then another year goes by."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 245210.0,
      "end_time": 246760.0,
      "text": "Two years go by."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 246760.0,
      "end_time": 248249.0,
      "text": "More specialists."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248249.0,
      "end_time": 250168.0,
      "text": "We take the kids to Italy."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250169.0,
      "end_time": 252638.0,
      "text": "We take the kids to Australia."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 252638.0,
      "end_time": 255350.0,
      "text": "And then more years pass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255350.0,
      "end_time": 257740.0,
      "text": "and the cancer begins to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 257740.0,
      "end_time": 260275.0,
      "text": "This time, there&#39;s new treatments on the horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 260274.0,
      "end_time": 262210.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re exotic. They&#39;re experimental."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 262211.0,
      "end_time": 265419.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to attack the cancer in new ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 265419.0,
      "end_time": 269745.0,
      "text": "So he enters a clinical trial, and it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 269745.0,
      "end_time": 271674.0,
      "text": "The cancer begins to shrink,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 271674.0,
      "end_time": 273950.0,
      "text": "and for the third time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 273951.0,
      "end_time": 277310.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve dodged death."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 277310.0,
      "end_time": 280607.0,
      "text": "So now I ask you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 280607.0,
      "end_time": 282996.0,
      "text": "how do I feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 282996.0,
      "end_time": 285510.0,
      "text": "when the time finally comes"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 285510.0,
      "end_time": 288150.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s another dark night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 288160.0,
      "end_time": 290517.0,
      "text": "sometime between midnight and 2 a.m.?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 290517.0,
      "end_time": 293491.0,
      "text": "This time it&#39;s on the intensive care ward"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 293491.0,
      "end_time": 295329.0,
      "text": "when a twentysomething resident"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 295329.0,
      "end_time": 297532.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve never met before"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 297532.0,
      "end_time": 300125.0,
      "text": "tells me that Terence is dying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 300125.0,
      "end_time": 302324.0,
      "text": "perhaps tonight."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 302324.0,
      "end_time": 305117.0,
      "text": "So what do I say when he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 305117.0,
      "end_time": 307931.0,
      "text": "\"What do you want me to do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 307931.0,
      "end_time": 309943.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s another drug out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 309943.0,
      "end_time": 311631.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s newer. It&#39;s more powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 311631.0,
      "end_time": 314200.0,
      "text": "He started it just two weeks ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 314200.0,
      "end_time": 317308.0,
      "text": "Perhaps there&#39;s still hope ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 317309.0,
      "end_time": 319264.0,
      "text": "So what do I say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 319264.0,
      "end_time": 322620.0,
      "text": "I say, \"Keep him alive if you can.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 322620.0,
      "end_time": 326135.0,
      "text": "And Terence died six days later."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 326135.0,
      "end_time": 330183.0,
      "text": "So we fought, we struggled, we triumphed."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 330183.0,
      "end_time": 331979.0,
      "text": "It was an exhilarating fight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 331979.0,
      "end_time": 333695.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d repeat the fight today"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 333696.0,
      "end_time": 336345.0,
      "text": "without a moment&#39;s hesitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 336345.0,
      "end_time": 339296.0,
      "text": "We fought together, we lived together."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 339296.0,
      "end_time": 341400.0,
      "text": "It turned what could have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 341400.0,
      "end_time": 344133.0,
      "text": "seven of the grimmest years of our life"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 344134.0,
      "end_time": 347745.0,
      "text": "into seven of the most glorious."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 347745.0,
      "end_time": 350520.0,
      "text": "It was also an expensive fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 350520.0,
      "end_time": 352481.0,
      "text": "It was the kind of fight and the kind of choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 352481.0,
      "end_time": 354115.0,
      "text": "that everyone here agrees"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 354115.0,
      "end_time": 356520.0,
      "text": "pump up the cost of end-of-life care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 356520.0,
      "end_time": 358806.0,
      "text": "and of healthcare for all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 358806.0,
      "end_time": 361888.0,
      "text": "And for me, for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 361888.0,
      "end_time": 363969.0,
      "text": "we pushed the fight right over the edge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 363970.0,
      "end_time": 367195.0,
      "text": "and I never got the chance to say to him"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 367195.0,
      "end_time": 370615.0,
      "text": "what I say to him now almost every day:"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 370615.0,
      "end_time": 373692.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, buddy, it was a hell of a ride.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 373692.0,
      "end_time": 376180.0,
      "text": "We never got the chance to say goodbye."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 376180.0,
      "end_time": 378459.0,
      "text": "We never thought it was the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 378459.0,
      "end_time": 383638.0,
      "text": "We always had hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 383638.0,
      "end_time": 387501.0,
      "text": "So what do we make of all of this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 387502.0,
      "end_time": 391800.0,
      "text": "Being a journalist, after Terence died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 391800.0,
      "end_time": 394369.0,
      "text": "I wrote a book, \"The Cost Of Hope.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 394369.0,
      "end_time": 396519.0,
      "text": "I wrote it because I wanted to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 396519.0,
      "end_time": 398205.0,
      "text": "why I did what I did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 398205.0,
      "end_time": 400600.0,
      "text": "why he did what he did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 400600.0,
      "end_time": 402561.0,
      "text": "why everyone around us did what they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 402561.0,
      "end_time": 404197.0,
      "text": "And what did I discover?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 404197.0,
      "end_time": 405771.0,
      "text": "Well, one of the things I discovered is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 405771.0,
      "end_time": 408848.0,
      "text": "experts think that one answer to"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 408848.0,
      "end_time": 411598.0,
      "text": "what I did at the end was a piece of paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 411598.0,
      "end_time": 413756.0,
      "text": "the advance directive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 413756.0,
      "end_time": 418950.0,
      "text": "to help families get past the seemingly irrational choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 418960.0,
      "end_time": 422210.0,
      "text": "Yet I had that piece of paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 422210.0,
      "end_time": 424263.0,
      "text": "We both did."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 424263.0,
      "end_time": 425953.0,
      "text": "And they were readily available."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 425953.0,
      "end_time": 427892.0,
      "text": "I had them right at hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 427892.0,
      "end_time": 430251.0,
      "text": "Both of them said the same thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 430251.0,
      "end_time": 434751.0,
      "text": "Do nothing if there is no further hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 434752.0,
      "end_time": 436972.0,
      "text": "I knew Terence&#39;s wishes"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 436972.0,
      "end_time": 440786.0,
      "text": "as clearly and as surely as I knew my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 440786.0,
      "end_time": 445990.0,
      "text": "Yet we never got to no further hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 445990.0,
      "end_time": 448747.0,
      "text": "Even with that clear-cut paper in our hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 448747.0,
      "end_time": 452300.0,
      "text": "we just kept redefining hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 452300.0,
      "end_time": 457294.0,
      "text": "I believed I could keep him from dying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 457295.0,
      "end_time": 460109.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d be embarrassed to say that if I hadn&#39;t seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 460109.0,
      "end_time": 462320.0,
      "text": "so many people and have talked to so many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 462320.0,
      "end_time": 464994.0,
      "text": "who have felt exactly the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 464994.0,
      "end_time": 468928.0,
      "text": "Right up until days before his death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 468928.0,
      "end_time": 472254.0,
      "text": "I felt strongly"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 472254.0,
      "end_time": 476297.0,
      "text": "and powerfully, and, you might say, irrationally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 476297.0,
      "end_time": 481544.0,
      "text": "that I could keep him from dying ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 481544.0,
      "end_time": 484779.0,
      "text": "Now, what do the experts call this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 484779.0,
      "end_time": 487126.0,
      "text": "They say it&#39;s denial."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 487126.0,
      "end_time": 489316.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a strong word, isn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 489317.0,
      "end_time": 491714.0,
      "text": "Yet I will tell you that denial"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 491714.0,
      "end_time": 496828.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t even close to a strong enough word"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 496828.0,
      "end_time": 499474.0,
      "text": "to describe what those of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 499474.0,
      "end_time": 503111.0,
      "text": "facing the death of our loved ones go through."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 503112.0,
      "end_time": 505453.0,
      "text": "And I hear the medical professionals say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 505453.0,
      "end_time": 507536.0,
      "text": "\"Well, we&#39;d like to do such-and-such,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 507536.0,
      "end_time": 509987.0,
      "text": "but the family&#39;s in denial."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 509987.0,
      "end_time": 512163.0,
      "text": "The family won&#39;t listen to reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 512163.0,
      "end_time": 514185.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re in denial."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 514183.99999999994,
      "end_time": 516535.99999999994,
      "text": "How can they insist on this treatment at the end?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 516537.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519841.00000000006,
      "text": "It&#39;s so clear, yet they&#39;re in denial.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 519841.0,
      "end_time": 521847.0,
      "text": "Now, I think this maybe isn&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 521847.0,
      "end_time": 524852.0,
      "text": "a very useful way of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 524852.0,
      "end_time": 527130.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just families either."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 527130.0,
      "end_time": 529255.0,
      "text": "The medical professionals too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 529255.0,
      "end_time": 532615.0,
      "text": "you out there, you&#39;re in denial too."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 532615.0,
      "end_time": 535468.0,
      "text": "You want to help. You want to fix."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 535468.0,
      "end_time": 537294.0,
      "text": "You want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 537294.0,
      "end_time": 540102.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve succeeded in everything you&#39;ve done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 540102.0,
      "end_time": 542144.0,
      "text": "and having a patient die,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 542144.0,
      "end_time": 545723.0,
      "text": "well, that must feel like failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 545723.0,
      "end_time": 547567.0,
      "text": "I saw it firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 547567.0,
      "end_time": 550269.0,
      "text": "Just days before Terence died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 550269.0,
      "end_time": 552287.0,
      "text": "his oncologist said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 552287.0,
      "end_time": 555535.0,
      "text": "\"Tell Terence that better days are just ahead.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 555535.0,
      "end_time": 557916.0,
      "text": "Days before he died."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 557917.0,
      "end_time": 559350.0,
      "text": "Yet Ira Byock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 559350.0,
      "end_time": 561698.0,
      "text": "the director of palliative medicine at Dartmouth"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 561698.0,
      "end_time": 564629.0,
      "text": "said, \"You know, the best doctor in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 564629.0,
      "end_time": 569237.0,
      "text": "has never succeeded in making anyone immortal.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 569237.0,
      "end_time": 575742.0,
      "text": "So what the experts call \"denial,\" I call \"hope,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 575743.0,
      "end_time": 578770.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d like to borrow a phrase"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 578770.0,
      "end_time": 581298.0,
      "text": "from my friends in software design."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 581298.0,
      "end_time": 584860.0,
      "text": "You just redefine denial and hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 584860.0,
      "end_time": 588880.0,
      "text": "and it becomes a feature of being human."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 588880.0,
      "end_time": 589949.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a bug."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 589949.0,
      "end_time": 592275.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a feature."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 592275.0,
      "end_time": 595369.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 595369.0,
      "end_time": 599630.0,
      "text": "So we need to think more constructively"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 599630.0,
      "end_time": 603375.0,
      "text": "about this very common, very profound"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 603375.0,
      "end_time": 607331.0,
      "text": "and very powerful human emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 607331.0,
      "end_time": 609955.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s part of the human condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 609955.0,
      "end_time": 612132.0,
      "text": "and yet our system and our thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 612132.0,
      "end_time": 615300.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t built to accommodate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 615301.0,
      "end_time": 618356.0,
      "text": "So Terence told me a story on that long-ago night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 618356.0,
      "end_time": 620261.0,
      "text": "and I believed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 620261.0,
      "end_time": 623375.0,
      "text": "Maybe I wanted to believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 623375.0,
      "end_time": 628704.0,
      "text": "And during Terence&#39;s illness, I, we,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 628704.0,
      "end_time": 630425.0,
      "text": "we wanted to believe the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 630426.0,
      "end_time": 633210.0,
      "text": "of our fight together too."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 633210.0,
      "end_time": 636757.0,
      "text": "Giving up the fight -- for that&#39;s how it felt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 636757.0,
      "end_time": 638695.0,
      "text": "it felt like giving up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 638696.0,
      "end_time": 641413.0,
      "text": "meant giving up not only his life"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 641413.0,
      "end_time": 645120.0,
      "text": "but also our story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 645120.0,
      "end_time": 647330.0,
      "text": "our story of us as fighters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 647330.0,
      "end_time": 650260.0,
      "text": "the story of us as invincible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 652468.0,
      "text": "and for the doctors, the story of themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 652468.0,
      "end_time": 655260.0,
      "text": "as healers."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 655260.0,
      "end_time": 657709.0,
      "text": "So what do we need?"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 657710.0,
      "end_time": 660649.0,
      "text": "Maybe we don&#39;t need a new piece of paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 660649.0,
      "end_time": 663596.0,
      "text": "Maybe we need a new story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 663596.0,
      "end_time": 667605.0,
      "text": "not a story about giving up the fight"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 667605.0,
      "end_time": 669876.0,
      "text": "or of hopelessness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 669876.0,
      "end_time": 673286.0,
      "text": "but rather a story of victory and triumph,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 673287.0,
      "end_time": 678130.0,
      "text": "of a valiant battle and, eventually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 678130.0,
      "end_time": 680450.0,
      "text": "a graceful retreat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 680450.0,
      "end_time": 683457.0,
      "text": "a story that acknowledges"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 683457.0,
      "end_time": 687220.0,
      "text": "that not even the greatest general defeats every foe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 687220.0,
      "end_time": 689841.0,
      "text": "that no doctor has ever succeeded"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 689841.0,
      "end_time": 692231.0,
      "text": "in making anyone immortal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 692231.0,
      "end_time": 698297.0,
      "text": "and that no wife, no matter how hard she tried,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 698297.0,
      "end_time": 702982.0,
      "text": "has ever stopped even the bravest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 702982.0,
      "end_time": 707310.0,
      "text": "wittiest and most maddeningly lovable husband"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 707310.0,
      "end_time": 711223.0,
      "text": "from dying when it was his time to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 711224.0,
      "end_time": 713537.0,
      "text": "People did mention hospice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 713537.0,
      "end_time": 716908.0,
      "text": "but I wouldn&#39;t listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 716908.0,
      "end_time": 720833.0,
      "text": "Hospice was for people who were dying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 720833.0,
      "end_time": 723606.0,
      "text": "and Terence wasn&#39;t dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 723606.0,
      "end_time": 726516.0,
      "text": "As a result, he spent just four days in hospice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 726516.0,
      "end_time": 728333.0,
      "text": "which I&#39;m sure, as you all know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 728333.0,
      "end_time": 730423.0,
      "text": "is a pretty typical outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 730423.0,
      "end_time": 731935.0,
      "text": "and we never said goodbye"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 731935.0,
      "end_time": 734989.0,
      "text": "because we were unprepared for the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 734990.0,
      "end_time": 738737.0,
      "text": "We have a noble path to curing the disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 738737.0,
      "end_time": 741670.0,
      "text": "patients and doctors alike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 741670.0,
      "end_time": 743190.0,
      "text": "but there doesn&#39;t seem to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 743190.0,
      "end_time": 745790.0,
      "text": "a noble path to dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 745790.0,
      "end_time": 748848.0,
      "text": "Dying is seen as failing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 748848.0,
      "end_time": 751500.0,
      "text": "and we had a heroic narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 751500.0,
      "end_time": 753593.0,
      "text": "for fighting together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 753593.0,
      "end_time": 758622.0,
      "text": "but we didn&#39;t have a heroic narrative for letting go."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 758623.0,
      "end_time": 762741.0,
      "text": "So maybe we need a narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 762741.0,
      "end_time": 766217.0,
      "text": "for acknowledging the end, and for saying goodbye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 766217.0,
      "end_time": 768779.0,
      "text": "and maybe our new story will be"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 768779.0,
      "end_time": 773385.0,
      "text": "about a hero&#39;s fight, and a hero&#39;s goodbye."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 773385.0,
      "end_time": 775852.0,
      "text": "Terence loved poetry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 775852.0,
      "end_time": 779790.0,
      "text": "and the Greek poet Constantine Cavafy"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 779790.0,
      "end_time": 781507.0,
      "text": "is one of my favorite poets."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 781508.0,
      "end_time": 784392.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ll give you a couple lines from him."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 784392.0,
      "end_time": 786608.0,
      "text": "This is a poem about Mark Antony."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 786608.0,
      "end_time": 789300.0,
      "text": "You know Mark Antony, the conquering hero,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 789301.0,
      "end_time": 791166.0,
      "text": "Cleopatra&#39;s guy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 791166.0,
      "end_time": 793703.0,
      "text": "Actually, one of Cleopatra&#39;s guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 793703.0,
      "end_time": 796127.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s been a pretty good general."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 796128.0,
      "end_time": 797188.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s won all the fights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 797188.0,
      "end_time": 799643.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s eluded all the people that are out to get him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 799643.0,
      "end_time": 801431.0,
      "text": "and yet this time, finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 801431.0,
      "end_time": 803180.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s come to the city of Alexandria"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 803180.0,
      "end_time": 804862.0,
      "text": "and realized he&#39;s lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 804862.0,
      "end_time": 806578.0,
      "text": "The people are leaving. They&#39;re playing instruments."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 806578.0,
      "end_time": 807901.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re singing."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 807901.0,
      "end_time": 810501.0,
      "text": "And suddenly he knows he&#39;s been defeated."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 810501.0,
      "end_time": 812680.0,
      "text": "And he suddenly knows"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 812680.0,
      "end_time": 815204.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s been deserted by the gods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 815205.0,
      "end_time": 817145.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s time to let go."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 817145.0,
      "end_time": 819112.0,
      "text": "And the poet tells him what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 819112.0,
      "end_time": 822377.0,
      "text": "He tells him how to say a noble goodbye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 822378.0,
      "end_time": 826225.0,
      "text": "a goodbye that&#39;s fit for a hero."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 826225.0,
      "end_time": 828974.0,
      "text": "\"As if long-prepared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 828974.0,
      "end_time": 831653.0,
      "text": "as if courageous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 831653.0,
      "end_time": 834250.0,
      "text": "as it becomes you"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 834250.0,
      "end_time": 836422.0,
      "text": "who were worthy of such a city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 836422.0,
      "end_time": 838825.0,
      "text": "approach the window with a firm step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 838825.0,
      "end_time": 841360.0,
      "text": "and with emotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 841360.0,
      "end_time": 843559.0,
      "text": "but not with the entreaties"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 843559.0,
      "end_time": 846319.0,
      "text": "or the complaints of a coward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 846320.0,
      "end_time": 848291.0,
      "text": "as a last enjoyment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 848291.0,
      "end_time": 850415.0,
      "text": "listen to the sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 850415.0,
      "end_time": 853748.0,
      "text": "the exquisite instruments of the musical troops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 853749.0,
      "end_time": 856300.0,
      "text": "and bid her farewell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 856300.0,
      "end_time": 860444.0,
      "text": "the Alexandria you are losing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 860445.0,
      "end_time": 864135.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a goodbye for a man who was larger than life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 864135.0,
      "end_time": 866153.0,
      "text": "a goodbye for a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 866153.0,
      "end_time": 868127.0,
      "text": "for whom anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 868127.0,
      "end_time": 871234.0,
      "text": "well, almost anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 871235.0,
      "end_time": 873125.0,
      "text": "was possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 873125.0,
      "end_time": 876265.0,
      "text": "a goodbye for a man who kept hope alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 876265.0,
      "end_time": 878458.0,
      "text": "And isn&#39;t that what we&#39;re missing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 878458.0,
      "end_time": 880516.0,
      "text": "How can we learn that people&#39;s decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 880517.0,
      "end_time": 882270.0,
      "text": "about their loved ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 882270.0,
      "end_time": 885956.0,
      "text": "are often based strongly, powerfully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 885956.0,
      "end_time": 888808.0,
      "text": "many times irrationally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 888808.0,
      "end_time": 891152.0,
      "text": "on the slimmest of hopes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 891152.0,
      "end_time": 894174.0,
      "text": "The overwhelming presence of hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 894174.0,
      "end_time": 895597.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t denial."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 895597.0,
      "end_time": 898417.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s part of our DNA as humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 898417.0,
      "end_time": 900735.0,
      "text": "and maybe it&#39;s time our healthcare system --"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 900735.0,
      "end_time": 905219.0,
      "text": "doctors, patients, insurance companies, us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 905219.0,
      "end_time": 909193.0,
      "text": "started accounting for the power of that hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 909193.0,
      "end_time": 911492.0,
      "text": "Hope isn&#39;t a bug."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 911493.0,
      "end_time": 913862.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a feature."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 913862.0,
      "end_time": 916357.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 916357.0,
      "end_time": 919411.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}